T02D3637:251a-1: he ru ka s'a dha nam /
T02D3637:251a-4: he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3637:251a-5: dur khrod brgyad kyi dbus gnas nas //
T02D3637:251a-6: zla med yid kyi dga' ba yi //
T02D3637:251a-7: thabs dang shes rab rnam pa yis //
T02D3637:251a-8: zla ba nyi ma rab sbyor bas ;
T02D3637:251a-9: / a'a li k'a li mnyam sbyor ba //
T02D3637:251a-10: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la bsgom bya //
T02D3637:251a-11: de la h'um yig las byung ba'i //
T02D3637:251a-12: rdo rje rtse gcig dang ldan pa //
T02D3637:251a-13: mi yi pags pa ro yi gdan //
T02D3637:251a-14: ro langs skyil krung phyed pas bzhugs //
T02D3637:251a-15: thal ba'i brdul gyis lus la byugs //
T02D3637:251a-16: rdo rje 'phro ba phyag g-yas na ;
T02D3637:251a-17: / ba dan g-yo bcas kha tv'am g-yon //
T02D3637:251a-18: thod pa dmar po dang bcas pa //
T02D3637:251a-19: brgya phyed mgo bo'i phreng ba yi //
T02D3637:251a-20: do shal yis ni 'phrog par byed //
T02D3637:251a-21: cung zad mche ba gtsigs pa'i zhal //
T02D3637:251a-22: spyan gsum pa ni sgeg bcas shing //
T02D3637:251a-23: dbu skra dmar ser gyen du brdzes //
T02D3637:251a-24: mi bskyod dbu rgyan rna rgyan dang //
T02D3637:251a-25: rus pa'i rgyan gyis mdzes byas shing //
T02D3637:251a-26: thod pa lnga yis dbu la brgyan //
T02D3637:251a-27: sangs rgyas nyid der bsgom par bya //
T02D3637:251a-29: aom h'um phat sv'a h'a zhes pa 'di mdor bsdus
